    "body": "Add a `-rpcid` CLI argument to `bitcoin-cli` that allows setting a custom string as the JSON-RPC request ID instead of the hardcoded default of 1. This enables correlating requests and responses when debugging or when multiple clients are making concurrent calls.\r\n\r\nOn the server side, include the request ID in the RPC debug log line when it differs from the default value of 1, so that custom IDs are visible in the `debug.log` output.\r\n\r\nTests are added in `test/functional/interface_bitcoin_cli.py` for this.",
